 German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aFiction. 4aErkenntnistheorie. 4aGeschichtstheorie. 4aWahrheit. 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978348670105040uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348670395540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486703955423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486703955/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012